  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Talent Acquisition Partner",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>Lead the end-to-end recruitment process for diverse roles across Trading, Operations, Marketing, and Technical functions, driving talent acquisition strategies that support business growth and innovation.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Lead full-cycle recruitment to attract and secure top talent for Trading, Operations, Marketing, and Technical roles, ensuring alignment with organizational goals.</li><li>Design and execute creative sourcing strategies across platforms including LinkedIn, Discord, Reddit, trading forums, and other social media to identify high-potential candidates.</li><li>Collaborate with hiring managers to define clear job scopes, refine candidate requirements, and develop structured, equitable interview processes that enhance candidate assessment.</li><li>Craft engaging job postings and outreach content that effectively communicate the employer value proposition to attract quality candidates.</li><li>Build and nurture strong relationships with candidates to ensure transparent communication and a positive recruitment experience throughout all stages.</li><li>Develop and maintain robust candidate pipelines for specialized and high-impact roles to meet current and future hiring demands.</li><li>Monitor market and talent trends within fintech, trading, and blockchain sectors to identify innovative sourcing opportunities and maintain competitive advantage.</li><li>Track, analyze, and report recruitment metrics and pipeline status to stakeholders, ensuring recruitment efforts meet hiring objectives.</li></ul><p><strong>Preferred competencies and qualifications</strong></p><ul><li>3+ years of recruitment experience, preferably within Cex, Dex, prop trading, or fintech sectors.</li><li>Proven ability to source and engage candidates through non-traditional channels such as Discord, Reddit, and community platforms.</li><li>Excellent communication, organizational, and relationship-building skills demonstrated through successful talent acquisition outcomes.</li><li>Proactive and agile mindset with the ability to thrive in a fast-scaling, dynamic environment.</li><li>Proficiency in English (written and spoken) is required to facilitate effective coordination and collaboration across internal teams and stakeholders in the Greater China region.</li></ul>",
